Installation Instructions
=========================

- Use the QuickInstaller tool or Plone's Control Panel 'Add/Remove
  Products' feature to install Archetypes, PortalTransforms,
  MimetypesRegistry and Calendaring

- Create a Calendar

- Create Events inside a Calendar

- Click on one of the Action Icons for Month/Week/Day views

- Alternatively, create a calendar in Apple's iCal application and use
  it's publishing feature to create a Calendar filled with Events
  straight into Plone
